      "Text": "Security update for avahi",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for avahi fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2026-34933: reachable assertion in `transport_flags_from_domain` can crash the `avahi-daemon` (bsc#1261546).\n- CVE-2026-24401: unsolicited mDNS responses containing a recursive CNAME record can crash the `avahi-daemon`\n  (bsc#1257235).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
